{
  "stem": "24651.3",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And we used to have fun, except that I had-- I don't know whether I had rickets or something, but I had trouble going on-- walking a lot.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "My, my joints were swollen, and I-- so I had trouble going on long trips.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Some of the children went to school, and-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] but they had a lot of bad experiences.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Beatings.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Stonings.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, I did not go to school.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And one time, men came on horseback with guns.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The older children, the teenagers, were equipped with guns, ammunition, and they defended the home.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they-- and the, you know, the attackers were-- went away.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So, [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] so-- but one day, when Lena-- we called Lena matka, mother.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And, and we, we felt like she was our mother.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know, my, my, my nickname was Krysza.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Oh, now I remember, [LAUGHS] Krysza.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And one day-- What does that mean?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It's diminutive for Krystina, Krysza.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] But one day, Lena went into town.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I had written a letter to Oscar Singer.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And she brought the letter to the refugee center.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "At that same time, my father, who had survived and was looking for me, came.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he saw the letter because he saw the name.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And that's how he found me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And Lena came and said, I have this wonderful news for you.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Your father has survived, and he'll be here now.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So-- and my father finally came.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I do.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I-- she took me-- Lena took me up to her office.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And my father came.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And when I first saw my father, I was absolutely terrified of him.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He looked like a skeleton.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I was terribly frightened.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I didn't want this strange person hugging me and kissing me.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
